    <tags>Cobertura,Plugin</tags>
    <reference><![CDATA[https://cobertura.github.io/cobertura/]]></reference>
    <reference><![CDATA[http://www.mojohaus.org/cobertura-maven-plugin/]]></reference>
    <parameters/>
    <code-examples>
